																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">22</div> <div class="vers-content">Cease ye therefore from the man, whose breath is in his nostrils, for he is reputed high.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">22</div> <div class="vers-content">Trouble mankind no more;  this at least man can boast, he has the breath of life in his nostrils.</div></div></td>
